"then release to <style=cIsUtility>Bless</style> an area for <style=cIsDamage>"
"12 seconds</style>, gradually <style=cIsHealing>restoring health</style> and "
"granting <style=cIsHealing>barrier</style> to all allies inside."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.PALADIN_SPECIAL_SCEPTERHEALZONE_NAME
msgid "Hallowed Sunlight"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.PALADIN_SPECIAL_SCEPTERHEALZONE_DESCRIPTION
